    {
      "q": "How do I find my advisor?",
      "a": "Log into myUIC, open Advising tab, access iAdvise."
    },
    {
      "q": "I have a registration hold, what do I do?",
      "a": "Check Student Self Service to identify the hold, then contact the responsible office."
    },
    {
      "q": "Where can I get extra help in my classes?",
      "a": "Start with instructor office hours, then use MSLC, Writing Center, or your college tutoring center."
